"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcpMW9fnNjGB2vWVwHYMevf6HJ4Xv4cBnPLRCZ4RVnAj9?filename=2O5QtzU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2O5QtzU.jpg&h=37a8a2a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好耐冇出過呢幅圖"},{"pid":"c02534dc132b90219cc326237c25cd69c4c7fb7d","tid":2487945,"uid":387907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:56:11.000Z","msg":"而家啲老細睇人咪睇談吐、語文、同埋儀表囉<br />\n<br />\n有錢人，著名牌上身，大大方方咁行<br />\n又夠膽企出嚟講嘢<br />\n<br />\n窮人，著住貴少少嘅都錫住錫住<br />\n又有啲唔同嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如葉瘤可以輕易咁放個幾十萬嘅袋喺地下<br />\n而老闆娘畀193話佢對鞋同水鞋差唔多樣就即爆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04e0e7bf0268d6428e1ecd7e494538f29e157c8","tid":2487945,"uid":27495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:57:56.000Z","msg":"不嬲錢係由上有錢嗰面分落去比人㗎啦<br />\n窮係食物鏈底層點會唔係最先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab3d309233c64edf73acaf7e03faf7e300a5e04","tid":2487945,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"佢做左幾多年人.<br />\n依家先知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41664cba1b7eb0ae389059248f858960bae65bb4","tid":2487945,"uid":165136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:11:10.000Z","msg":"「能力同係窮無關係的。」<br />\n啱<br />\n打工同能力無關係的"},{"pid":"4f8bf5ed4f9aa92f5b3b08378abfc00f4c564ffd","tid":2487945,"uid":267658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ab3d309233c64edf73acaf7e03faf7e300a5e04","tid":2487945,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"佢做左幾多年人.<br />\n依家先知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"依個世界上,係乜野人都有<br />\n<br />\n不過,唔緊要啦!<br />\n反正,班有錢人的職位遲早都會被中國共產黨員取代"},{"pid":"edd81d6bd894f5d1825dd4ac47a1daa51aac3edd","tid":2487945,"uid":204489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"因為有錢人個個都有份叫 兒子 既職業"},{"pid":"62c67a07b150d5c01a0206baa6b72d292ddc7b36","tid":2487945,"uid":80902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6c7ae22b803f2d32e085f0c7b5116f7d906e6bf","tid":2487945,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5052e6da9ed02fabd57208840bb97f378ceaef77","tid":2487945,"uid":86898,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「老闆請人都係請有能力，理得你有無錢。」<br />\n「能力同係窮無關係的。」<br />\n「請人不是按最有資格來的，是按能力來的，社會會懲罰不努力的人！」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度網民，咁撚弱智都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"講依D果D咪係有錢人，依為乜都係講自己努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日狐假虎威以為真係自己勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連自己都呃埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:19:17.000Z","msg":"努力唔係必定有回報，但努力係向上流同keep住留係上流既基本<br />\n<br />\n我以前都係你呢種諗法，但過多幾年後就發現自己比同期差唔多背景既人落後。之後真係好努力先追得返上去。<br />\n送多一句：你必須好撚努力，才能看起來毫不費力。"},{"pid":"b9ec667b17e663536c3d7bd4c298764833a198ed","tid":2487945,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:19:19.000Z","msg":"公司出賤價請人， 窮人會睇人工， 有錢人本身有錢， 打工為過日晨， 所以唔care 人工， 就算賤價都一樣照做， 所以搵工一定心易"},{"pid":"e733369268b7cc7e8e7b82e3e00d9aa9a7ba8a12","tid":2487945,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"其實跟車搬貨都等人用，唔嫌辛苦就得"}]}